                                                                                              PE-05           ACCESS CONTROL FOR OUTPUT DEVICES
                                                                                                              ASSESSMENT OBJECTIVE:
                                                                                                              Determine if:

                                                                                                              PE-05_ODP            output devices that require physical access control to output are deﬁned;

                                                                                                              PE-05                physical access to output from <PE-05_ODP output devices> is controlled to
                                                                                                                                   prevent unauthorized individuals from obtaining the output.

                                                                                                              POTENTIAL ASSESSMENT METHODS AND OBJECTS:
                                                                                                              PE-05-Examine        [SELECT FROM: Physical and environmental protecon policy; procedures
                                                                                                                                   addressing access control for display medium; facility layout of system components;
                                                                                                                                   actual displays from system components; list of output devices and associated
                                                                                                                                   outputs requiring physical access controls; physical access control logs or records
                                                                                                                                   for areas containing output devices and related outputs; system security plan;
                                                                                                                                   other relevant documents or records].

